dat %>%
  select(date, Office, Industrial, Retail, Apartment, Hotel, Land) %>%
  tidyr::gather(key, value, -date) %>%
  mutate(value=ifelse(is.na(value), 0, value),
         date=as.Date(sprintf("%d-01-01", date))) -> sg_dat

sg_dat %>%
  streamgraph() %>%
  sg_axis_x(1, "year", "%Y") %>%
  sg_colors("PuOr")
